explained very readily by the fact

00:53:10.930 --> 00:53:14.330
that what was being
legislated against was sodomy.

00:53:14.330 --> 00:53:17.480
And sodomy was principally
a sin committed between --

00:53:17.480 --> 00:53:21.040
or it was exclusively a sin
committed between two men.

00:53:21.040 --> 00:53:22.710
