00:53:38.990 --> 00:53:43.620
by Alfonso X in the 13th
century, or complied by order

00:53:43.620 --> 00:53:49.040
of Alfonso X. This
is the iconic title

00:53:49.040 --> 00:53:53.100
which condemns the vice
or the sin of sodomy.

00:53:53.100 --> 00:53:56.780
